replies.body:
Don't dare to defend LB, she is the same BS that Ahri is, perhaps even worst pre lv6.
2 Dashs with a possible return and a passive that makes her invisible for on second and gives her a outplay potencial with her clone.

I hate playing against champions that have kits that allow them to fck up everything and still not be punished, and our new recent addition to this list is this thing: {{champion:84}}

That's funny cause I never had problems with an enemy Ahri in months. 

I ether stomp her in lane with my other mid lane picks or I'm playing support so she will just get cc by me the instant she makes a move.

Oh well if she gets nerfed that's just more freelo when the enemy team picks her {{sticker:sg-jinx}}
